## Data Cleaning and Preparation

### Initial Inspection

- Loaded the dataset and printed its shape and column names  
- Previewed the first few rows and checked for missing values

### Country Filtering

- Removed non-sovereign entities and aggregate regions (e.g., "World", "Asia", "European Union")  
- Replaced ambiguous entries (e.g., "Congo" changed to "Republic of the Congo")  
