### Time Range Restriction

- Filtered data to include only years from 1992 to 2022  
- Saved the cleaned subset as `df_final_92.csv`

### Columns Selected for Analysis

The following 25 columns were retained to answer key questions:

- Identifiers: `country`, `iso_code`, `year`  
- Demographics and Economy: `population`, `gdp`  
- Emissions Volume: `co2`, `co2_per_capita`, `co2_growth_abs`, `co2_growth_prct`  
- Emissions Sources: `coal_co2`, `oil_co2`, `gas_co2`, `cement_co2`, `flaring_co2`, `land_use_change_co2`  
- Energy Metrics: `primary_energy_consumption`, `energy_per_capita`, `energy_per_gdp`, `co2_per_unit_energy`, `co2_per_gdp`  
